== Gingko ==
by Christian Carter -- PACE, NEQBA, Emerson College '13

Start off with an easy way to keep track of who your teams are.
Add tracking of phases and brackets.
Quick round robins from there.
Printable schedules.
Other easy document production built in.
Statistics all rolled up in there.

== Usage ==
script/server
http://localhost:3000/setup/home

== Pre-reqs ==
Rails, sqlite

== What's next ==
* Actually handle statistics
* A user system with proper authentication
* Buzzer tracking simplified
* Abstraction of the concept of "rounds"
* Make it clean, make it pretty

